txt.en: The leader of the Woodworker's Guild has asked you to build a cart to transport all the chairs ordered for the reconstruction efforts.
The crafting recipes you must create can be bartered for from the Improved Recipes vendor.\n\nBuild a guild-pattern cart.
Execute the recipe for a guild-pattern cart
'Well this is an amusing problem. We finally made all the chairs, but we don't have enough carts to load and transport them. Make one please.'
Executed the recipe for a guild-pattern cart ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
'Well this is an amusing problem. We finally made all the chairs, but we don't have enough carts to load and transport them. Make one please.'
Turn in a guild-pattern cart to Viola Brockhouse
'We'll start dispatching our goods right away. Thank you very much.'
Talk to the Woodworker's Guild Leader in Minas Morgul
Turn in a guild-pattern cart to the Woodworker's Guild Leader in Minas Morgul
'We'll start dispatching our goods right away. Thank you very much.'
